c: 28
v: 23
t: "And when he arrived at the watering place of Midian he found there a lot of men watering their animals. And he found two women, apart from the men, holding their flocks back. He asked, \"What is the matter with you two?\" The two said, \"We cannot water our flocks till the shepherds lead theirs' away from the water. And our father is a very old man"